com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface LocalSubordinate

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject, ReplicationSubordinate
public interface LocalSubordinate
extends ReplicationSubordinate

Represents a local subordinate site definition. This interface specifies the details of a local subordinate project where the master will replicate items.
